						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone set up near the Garuḍa pillar in front of the Hanumān temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record mentions <hi rend="bold">Kadimriḍi</hi> (the present Kadarmanḍalgi) and seems to record a grant of land. The other details are not clear. It is engraved in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.</hi> </p>						

						</summary>
